The paper deals with power allocation in a wireless network, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). The paper also mentions game theory, which falls under the sub-category of Game Theory and Economics (cs.GT). The use of trial and error learning and the decentralized algorithm suggests that the paper may also fall under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
